                            | mode. The user can now follow a designated path up the mountain terrain, outside of the garden, that leads to a hot springs. Although the user
                            | cannot feel the water in the hot springs, it is very cool to see how the hands can still interact with the water. We also had some user feedback
                            | that the orange color of the lanterns during meditation mode may not be right for everyone so the hot springs mediation mode has blue lights in
