                            a(href='') here.
                        h3 Successes and Accomplishments From This Week
                        p 
                            | After realizing that there are many controls that players must know to fully take
                            | advantage of the application, Hristo added an introduction scene that the player
                            | is loaded into on startup. The player now comes in outside the garden in a shrine
